<%- include('partials/head') %>
<%- include('partials/nav') %>

<main class="page-content">
  <section class="hero" style="padding-bottom:60px;">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="hero-content fade-in">
        <span class="overline">About</span>
        <h1>Ore Phillips Advisory <span class="text-muted" style="font-size:0.5em;vertical-align:middle;">(dba Orphil LLC)</span></h1>
        <p class="lead">AI Transformation Partner for Finance, Accounting & Consulting Firms.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="about-content">
        <div>
          <h2>The Mission</h2>
          <p style="margin-bottom:24px;">Orphil exists to help finance, accounting, and consulting firms adopt AI with confidence — not through hype, but through practical strategy, real advisory, and hands-on execution.</p>
          <p style="margin-bottom:24px;">Founded by Ore Phillips, Orphil bridges the gap between what AI can do and what finance professionals need it to do. We understand the domain, the constraints, and the opportunity.</p>
          <p>Every engagement starts with where you are today and builds toward where you need to go. We don't sell tooling or platforms — we build capabilities, deploy real solutions, and leave your team stronger than we found it.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="belief-block" style="margin-top:0;">
            <blockquote>"<%= belief %>"</blockquote>
            <cite>— The Orphil Belief</cite>
          </div>

          <div class="card" style="margin-top:24px;">
            <h4 style="margin-bottom:16px;">What We Build Toward</h4>
            <p>The goal of every engagement is to leave the client more capable, not more dependent. Orphil builds toward its own redundancy.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Internal vs External -->
  <section>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <span class="overline">The Multiplier</span>
        <h2>Internal & external AI transformation</h2>
        <p>For firms that serve other companies, Orphil's services apply in two directions — and that's the multiplier.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="card-grid">
        <div class="card">
          <h3>Internal — Your Firm</h3>
          <ul style="list-style:none;padding:0;margin-top:16px;">
            <li style="padding:6px 0;color:var(--text-secondary);">&#8226; Train your own staff and leadership on AI</li>
            <li style="padding:6px 0;color:var(--text-secondary);">&#8226; Build internal agents that make consultants more productive</li>
            <li style="padding:6px 0;color:var(--text-secondary);">&#8226; Develop your AI roadmap as a firm</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3>External — Your Clients</h3>
          <ul style="list-style:none;padding:0;margin-top:16px;">
            <li style="padding:6px 0;color:var(--text-secondary);">&#8226; Deliver AI strategy and roadmap services to your client base</li>
            <li style="padding:6px 0;color:var(--text-secondary);">&#8226; Build agents and tools for clients under your brand</li>
            <li style="padding:6px 0;color:var(--text-secondary);">&#8226; Position your firm as the AI transformation partner clients turn to first</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <p style="margin-top:32px;font-size:1.05rem;color:var(--text-secondary);max-width:680px;">Every internal capability you build also becomes a service you can offer clients.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section style="text-align:center;">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Let's talk about your AI transformation.</h2>
      <p style="margin:16px auto 32px;">Whether you're just starting or ready to scale — we'll meet you where you are.</p>
      <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Get in Touch &rarr;</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</main>

<%- include('partials/footer') %>
